# Sovereign State: Global Hegemony

A browser-based geopolitical simulator built for js13k 2024.

## Features

- 🗺️ **Interactive World Map** - Hex-based nation display with pan/zoom
- 🏛️ **Government** - View leader info, cabinet overview, threat assessment
- 💰 **Economy** - Adjust budget sliders across 6 departments
- ⚔️ **Military** - Manage armed forces and defense spending
- 🤝 **Diplomacy** - Track relations with 9 world nations
- 🕵️ **Intelligence** - Monitor covert ops and threat intel
- 🚀 **Space Program** - Progress towards Mars mission
- 📰 **Dynamic News Ticker** - Random world events affect gameplay
- ⏱️ **Speed Controls** - Pause, 1×, 2×, 5×, or 10× simulation
- 📱 **Responsive** - Works on desktop and mobile

## How to Play

Open `index.html` in any modern browser. Click a speed button to start the simulation - each turn advances one month. Adjust budget sliders to influence your treasury and national performance. Monitor the news ticker for random events that affect your nation.

## Tech

Pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript - zero dependencies. Canvas-based map rendering.
